   - 3D: per-depth-level based on temperature data availability
   - Could add as computed fields in fmeDerivedFields or fmeDepthCoarsening

3. ELM FME INTEGRATION (DEFERRED)
   - elm_fme_derived.F90 and elm_fme_vcoarsen.F90 were removed due to build
     issues (histFileMod internals private, ptr_gcell pointer constraints).
   - Reimplementation path: pass ELM state pointers directly to the register
     function (avoid histFileMod internals); use col_ptr_t wrapper pattern
     for hist_addfld1d pointer arguments.
   - Fields of interest: TSOI, H2OSOI, SOILICE (vcoarsen), TOTAL_SOIL_WATER (derived)
   - Shell_commands already has the namelist options, just commented out.

4. MOSART FME INTEGRATION (DEFERRED)
   - RtmFmeDerived.F90 was removed due to build issues (mpicom vs mpicom_rof,
     ptr_rof pointer constraints).
   - Reimplementation path: use mpicom_rof throughout; use col_ptr_t wrapper
     pattern for RtmHistAddfld pointer arguments.
   - Fields of interest: QSUR_LIQ, QSUB_LIQ, VOLR_LIQ, RUNOFFLND_LIQ, etc.
   - Shell_commands already has the namelist options, just commented out.

